      "raw_text": "Judge H. L. KEENAN, today enter\ned his judgment in the case of the\nSpokane Valley Land & Water Co.\nagainst Arthur d. Jones and the\nLiberty Lake Irrigation Co., which\nhas been In litigation for six or\neight years.\n\n\nIn trial some years ago Jones\nwas awarded $4,000 damages, bit\nthe supreme court overturned the\nJudgment. In today's findings Jones\nis tivon $4,000 Tor the land involved\nand no damages, and the case will\nlikely again 60 up."
